Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0

Package: nos-apps-runtime
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         docker-ce | docker.io,
         docker-ce-cli | docker.io,
         containerd.io | containerd,
         docker-buildx-plugin,
         docker-compose-plugin | docker-compose,
         acl,
         rsync,
         curl,
         jq
Recommends: btrfs-progs
Description: NithronOS Apps Runtime - Docker-based application platform
 Provides a hardened Docker runtime for NithronOS applications with:
 - Pre-configured Docker daemon with security defaults
 - Btrfs-aware snapshot support for app data
 - Systemd integration for app lifecycle management
 - CLI helpers for container operations
 .
 This package sets up the Docker environment, creates necessary
 directories, and provides tools for managing containerized
 applications on NithronOS.
